  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/4936195af810c1f8f3716bd772840140.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/4936195af810c1f8f3716bd772840140.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/4936195af810c1f8f3716bd772840140.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We Heist Too is a 3D sandbox open-world game set in the quirky, atomic 1960s-inspired city of Rywadorium, where you step into the shoes of a thief leading a double life as a seemingly ordinary citizen. The game blends elements of stealth, adventure, puzzle-solving, and RPG, offering players a rich playground to explore and experiment with various criminal playstyles without quest markers, encouraging creativity and problem-solving in how you approach each heist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/b1ecbd1df0b915360ba0672fa1bd0317.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/b1ecbd1df0b915360ba0672fa1bd0317.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/b1ecbd1df0b915360ba0672fa1bd0317.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features include:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open-world exploration:</strong> Roam diverse city regions, interact with numerous objects and environments, and discover resources that can aid your heists or hinder you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple playstyles:</strong> Choose to be a stealthy mastermind, sneaky and unseen, or a bold outlaw who uses brute force and guns blazing; your decisions impact gameplay and consequences</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic interactions:</strong> Engage with citizens, decide how to talk or manipulate them, and rely on your partner in crime, Bernard Maidenhoff, for tips and support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource management and customization:</strong> Visit shops, gas stations, and workshops to buy or acquire equipment like gliders or lockpicks, or procure gear from the black market to enhance your thieving capabilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/ac4cfb09b6b12d18d9397697d57f0a2d.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/ac4cfb09b6b12d18d9397697d57f0a2d.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/ac4cfb09b6b12d18d9397697d57f0a2d.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique setting and tone:</strong> The game’s art style and world draw inspiration from titles like Atomic Heart, Bioshock, and We Happy Few, mixing surreal, dark humor with a retro-futuristic 60s vibe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Consequences and challenges:</strong> Getting caught by police or robots has serious repercussions, adding tension and stakes to your criminal endeavors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/6d80e70b25edf68dc0e2b3fa3bc67d27.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/6d80e70b25edf68dc0e2b3fa3bc67d27.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/6d80e70b25edf68dc0e2b3fa3bc67d27.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overall, We Heist Too offers a sandbox thief simulator experience with stealth, puzzle, and RPG elements wrapped in a colorful, surreal, and humorous atomic 60s world. It invites players to craft their own criminal stories with freedom and creativity, making each heist a unique challenge and adventure.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/4936195af810c1f8f3716bd772840140.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/4936195af810c1f8f3716bd772840140.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/4936195af810c1f8f3716bd772840140.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We Heist Too is a 3D sandbox open-world game set in the quirky, atomic 1960s-inspired city of Rywadorium, where you step into the shoes of a thief leading a double life as a seemingly ordinary citizen. The game blends elements of stealth, adventure, puzzle-solving, and RPG, offering players a rich playground to explore and experiment with various criminal playstyles without quest markers, encouraging creativity and problem-solving in how you approach each heist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/b1ecbd1df0b915360ba0672fa1bd0317.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/b1ecbd1df0b915360ba0672fa1bd0317.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/b1ecbd1df0b915360ba0672fa1bd0317.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features include:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open-world exploration:</strong> Roam diverse city regions, interact with numerous objects and environments, and discover resources that can aid your heists or hinder you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Multiple playstyles:</strong> Choose to be a stealthy mastermind, sneaky and unseen, or a bold outlaw who uses brute force and guns blazing; your decisions impact gameplay and consequences</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic interactions:</strong> Engage with citizens, decide how to talk or manipulate them, and rely on your partner in crime, Bernard Maidenhoff, for tips and support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Resource management and customization:</strong> Visit shops, gas stations, and workshops to buy or acquire equipment like gliders or lockpicks, or procure gear from the black market to enhance your thieving capabilities</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/ac4cfb09b6b12d18d9397697d57f0a2d.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/ac4cfb09b6b12d18d9397697d57f0a2d.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/ac4cfb09b6b12d18d9397697d57f0a2d.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique setting and tone:</strong> The game’s art style and world draw inspiration from titles like Atomic Heart, Bioshock, and We Happy Few, mixing surreal, dark humor with a retro-futuristic 60s vibe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Consequences and challenges:</strong> Getting caught by police or robots has serious repercussions, adding tension and stakes to your criminal endeavors</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/6d80e70b25edf68dc0e2b3fa3bc67d27.poster.avif?t=1773525519\" width=1170 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/6d80e70b25edf68dc0e2b3fa3bc67d27.webm?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008210/extras/6d80e70b25edf68dc0e2b3fa3bc67d27.mp4?t=1773525519\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overall, We Heist Too offers a sandbox thief simulator experience with stealth, puzzle, and RPG elements wrapped in a colorful, surreal, and humorous atomic 60s world. It invites players to craft their own criminal stories with freedom and creativity, making each heist a unique challenge and adventure.</p>",
